<p>Let \(x=-d\) be the directrix for the 2 below conics, and \(e\) be their eccentricity. Drag the sliders on the graphs below to create the following curves (Note that the red dashed line is \(x=-d\)): </p>

<p>\(r = e^{-{@rand2*theta@}}\)</p>
[[jsxgraph input-ref-ans2='ans2Ref']]
var board = JXG.JSXGraph.initBoard(divid, {
            boundingbox: [-1.1, 1.1, 1.1, -1.1],
            keepaspectratio: true,
            showCopyright: false,
            axis: true,
            showNavigation: true,
